She thought, I must be getting soft in the spark or something.

She took Dollen by the arm and put his arm over her shoulder to help 
him walk. "Don't argue.  Your not exactly in great shape and we have 
a long walk ahead of us."  She tried to help support him as shew 
walked with him.
